PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F387A1762020001
OL,3,CFormer UK Border chief says ETA
OL,4,Cloophole poses 'risk' for authorities
OL,6,F"Provided that you have immigration
OL,7,Fofficers checking these documents,
OL,8,Fthey will be trained in forgeries and
OL,9,Fhave powers to send people back to
OL,10,FFrance if they have incorrect
OL,11,Fdocuments, then I think we can trust
OL,12,Fthem.
OL,14,F"We don't want border controls between
OL,15,Fthe UK, the islands and Ireland, we
OL,16,Fhaven't had them before but we need to
OL,17,Fbe alert to new threats."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
