OL,3,CFormer UK Border chief says ETA
OL,4,Cloophole poses 'risk' for authorities
OL,6,FMr Smith's comments follow an
OL,7,Fannouncement by Guernsey's government
OL,8,Fthat the French day-tripper scheme has
OL,9,Fbeen extended into 2026, despite
OL,10,Fearlier concerns that it would be
OL,11,Fincompatible with the UK's new ETA
OL,12,Frequirements.
OL,14,FHe says: "The UK has introduced a
OL,15,Funiversal Electronic Travel
OL,16,FAuthorisation system now for anybody
OL,17,Fcoming to the UK who doesn't have a
OL,18,FBritish or Irish passport, including
OL,19,FEU citizens.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
