CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F387A1762020001
OL,3,CFormer UK Border chief says ETA
OL,4,Cloophole poses 'risk' for authorities
OL,6,F"If someone can go into Guernsey
OL,7,Fwithout an ETA to potentially come on
OL,8,Fto the UK without one, then that is a
OL,9,Fpotential risk."
OL,11,FHowever, Guernsey officials insist
OL,12,Fthat robust safeguards will prevent
OL,13,Fanyone from boarding a flight or boat
OL,14,Fto the UK while visiting the island
OL,15,Fthrough the day-tripper scheme.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, the Government of Jersey
OL,18,Fsays it is preparing to extend its
OL,19,Fsimilar French ID card day visitor
OL,20,Finitiative, with rule changes
OL,21,Fcurrently being worked on.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
