OL,3,CFormer UK Border chief says ETA
OL,4,Cloophole poses 'risk' for authorities
OL,6,FOn how the UK Home Office may monitor
OL,7,Fthe situation, Mr Smith adds: "I
OL,8,Fsuspect they will be watching the
OL,9,Ftraffic that's coming in from the
OL,10,FChannel Islands and through the Common
OL,11,FTravel Area to see if there is any
OL,12,Fabuse or concerns.
OL,14,F"I don't think we've heard the end of
OL,15,Fit, but I don't think for the time
OL,16,Fbeing people need to worry too much
OL,17,Fabout this. I don't think it's a major
OL,18,Fthreat to the UK border in the grand
OL,19,Fscheme of things.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
