CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F387A1762020001
OL,3,CFormer UK Border chief says ETA
OL,4,Cloophole poses 'risk' for authorities
OL,6,F"I know there's very good
OL,7,Fcommunication between the Channel
OL,8,FIslands and the UK Home Office.
OL,10,F"Looking at the risk posed by this,
OL,11,Fwhen balanced against the risk to
OL,12,Flocal companies there who rely a lot
OL,13,Fupon day-trippers to fund their
OL,14,Fbusinesses, then I suppose a pragmatic
OL,15,Fdecision seems to be the right one but
OL,16,FI suspect we'll keep an eye on it."
OL,18,FITV News has contacted the UK Home
OL,19,FOffice for comment.
